%^YELLOW%^Skill: Athletics

%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^A player's athletics skill indicates their aptitude at various physical activities requiring speed, precision and/or reflexes. It would cover areas of jumping, climbing, rolling, and horseback abilities. Since Athletics on Sundering Shadows include both athletics and acrobatics from the tabletop source, it will use either dexterity or strength, whichever is higher, for your character.

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Stat basis: %^WHITE%^dexterity or strength
%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Current areas of influence: %^WHITE%^climbing, riding, scramble, reflection

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Related helpfiles: %^WHITE%^skills, horses, scramble, reflection *feats
